OL,3,CManchester City's Nico O'Reilly named
OL,4,CPremier League Young Player of the
OL,5,CSeason
OL,7,FManchester City defender Nico O'Reilly
OL,8,Fhas been named Premier League Young
OL,9,FPlayer of the Season.
OL,11,FThe versatile full back is a product
OL,12,Fof the club's academy and has featured
OL,13,Fin 34 Premier League games, scoring
OL,14,Ffive goals and creating three assists.
OL,16,FHe's been a key part in ensuring Pep
OL,17,FGuardiola's final season at the club
OL,18,Fwas a successful one, scoring two
OL,19,Fgoals in the League Cup final in March
OL,20,Fto deliver City's first trophy of the
OL,21,F2025/26 season.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
