PN,39302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779628274
OL,3,CManchester City's Nico O'Reilly named
OL,4,CPremier League Young Player of the
OL,5,CSeason
OL,7,FHis performances have earned him a
OL,8,Fplace in the England squad for the
OL,9,FWorld Cup in June and July 2026.
OL,11,FO'Reilly said: "I'm very proud to have
OL,12,Fwon this award. After my first
OL,13,Fappearances in senior football last
OL,14,Fseason, I knew this year I could have
OL,15,Fthe opportunity to play more and help
OL,16,Fthe team as much as possible if I
OL,17,Fworked hard.
OL,26,@sD@POU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
