OL,3,CManchester City's Nico O'Reilly named
OL,4,CPremier League Young Player of the
OL,5,CSeason
OL,7,F"And the City fans... they have been
OL,8,Funbelievable. I've really felt their
OL,9,Fsupport, so thank you to all of them."
OL,11,FManchester City host Aston Villa at
OL,12,Fthe Etihad Stadium on Sunday 24 May to
OL,13,Fclose out their season and bid
OL,14,Ffarewell to manager Pep Guardiola.
